h1.div: Welcome to Lunenburg County Public Schools Learning Portal

div.p: Due to the Governor's announcement of closing schools for the remainder of the year, LCPS has developed a plan moving forward with guidance from VDOE. Our teachers and administrators have provided these resources to keep learning alive at home. New activities will be posted on April 20th for five weeks of instruction. We will continue to update this portal. Please stay updated on our website and LCPS Facebook page. We are thinking about you and we miss YOU!
